00:50:51,069 --> 00:50:52,969
Des mensonges.

844
00:50:54,639 --> 00:50:56,402
De la peur.

845
00:51:00,812 --> 00:51:02,803
De la mort.

846
00:51:06,384 --> 00:51:08,215
